{
  "stem": "521.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Koszeg.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kojak is dead.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He died a year ago.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was my favorite.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the Hungarians liked or disliked the Jew was coming without anything on the train.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he wants to cause him trouble.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was hoping that somebody's going to shoot me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, how are we going?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The hair is OK?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Good.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I enjoy it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No that was in a combination concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were taken, but before we were taken, we have been put on a-- a-- a cattle wagon.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were about 80 people in the wagon, which would have been comfortable for about 20, maybe less.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, before we-- There were safe houses in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now there was one by the Vatican, and one by the Swiss, and the third one was the real one by the Swiss.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was Wallenstein-- Wallenstein.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wallenberg, he wasn't Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Wallenberg and he has given out various documents for Jews, and if somebody was taken by the Hungarian police or this extreme rightist, and he has shown this Wallenberg document, he was either let go or he was shot.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that was an easy choice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But at least somebody had a chance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe he is going to be let go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were some apartment buildings, which were rented by the Swedish Embassy where Jews were safe.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's why they called it the safe house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now there was a man sitting in the dark with a light beaming from behind him, and he was yelling while we were putting in the wagon, if you have a Swedish-- Swedish papers, Swedish pass, then just come to me, and even if yours was destroyed.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he had a book in front of him with all the names who were-- who had--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Outside the wagon, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The what?",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
